replyContent: Hi Tyler, you can save to Google drive on free version and restore from Google drive on paid version. Regards, Karl.

I love this app. I have been able to match my 1098 and loan disclosures to this app down to the penny. There are also amortization tables. I love numbers and I feel like this app gives me the power to easily deal with lenders quickly so I can double check what I am being told. Get this app!

content: I have used Karl's mortgage calculator for literally years (since ADP1) and have found it invaluable. I am happy to pay for it.
Great app for seeing how much I can save on interest by paying a little extra on the mortgage or by getting a lower rate.
I'm glad I purchased this app. I used it again and again to help decide between loans... and I'm saving Tens of Thousands of dollars on my mortgage now!! =D
Outstanding program.  Covers almost any facet of mortgage payment/calculation.  Simple to use gui/format with ability to add changes easily, and quickly.  HIGHLY recommend for anyone in real estate.
Tried a lot of similar apps and in the end, it's the best one there is.

I love this app! It is so easy to use and it makes you realize how much money you are blowing on interest. It has amazing features like "extra payments, one time payments". What do I have to pay to get my note to end in 5 years, etc. I strongly recommend this for reviewing any debt with interest like car loans, home loans, credit cards, etc. It shows you that even a small extra payment each month can knock years off your house mortgage.
Simple and easy to use.

I've used Karl's Mortgage Calculator, accessing the allocation their website, for many years.  Now I have the same application using Android... How wonderful!  This app is perfect, easy to use and the calculations and end results area always accurate.  I highly recommend this app!
